<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>95</hymn_number>
<title>WHAT A WONDERFUL SAVIOUR</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Krista'n gitloh khuhna A siem,
 Hukdampa mak ahi ie;
 Man pieka tat in I um tau,
 Hukdampa mak ahi ie!

[V2]
 Hukdampa mak kha Isu ahi, ka Lal Isu
 Hukdampa mak kha Isu ahi, ka Lalpa.

[V3]
 2. Thienna thisan zalin ka pak,
 Hukdampa mak ahi ie;
 Pathien tawh ei kicham-sak tai,
 Hukdampa mak ahi ie!

[V4]
 3. Ka lungthim gitloh A sawp thieng,
 Hukdampa mak ahi ie!
 Tu'n ka lunggil ah vai a hawm,
 Hukdampa mak ahi ie!

[V5]
 4. Ka chiehna ah ei kitawnpih,
 Hukdampa mak ahi ie!
 Nicheng in ginum di'n ei veng,
 Hukdampa mak ahi ie!

[V6]
 5. Zawhna thilhih theihna ei pie'i,
 Hukdampa mak ahi ie!
 Thepna hunah guol ei zawh sak,
 Hukdampa mak ahi ie!

[V7]
 6. Ka lunggil cheng Amah ka pie'i,
 Hukdampa mak ahi ie!
 Khawvel thillam ngaihtuoh puo'ng ka,
 Hukdampa mak ahi ie!</lyrics>
</song>